Special Techniques

In this 30 minute film of the special techniques, additional movements are shown to enhance the techniques taught in the basic class. The  special techniques can be used later in application to various pathologies. If these techniques are targeted for use, they support the healing process of specific pathologies. The special techniques need to be applied with the basic sequences. You will be able to practice the sequences well by following this DVD or video.
